    h1 EC Motor Controls
    br
    br
    .row
        .col.product-image
            img.product-photos(src='../src/photos/products-photos/ECM 3PT.gif' alt='3PT Controller')
        .col.product-description
            h5 EVO/™ECM-3PT (3 Point Floating Control Unit)
            ul
                li Increase/decrease control for EC Motors.
                li Adjustable Rate.
                li 0-10V feedback.
                li Status and Flow Index Lamps.
                li OEM and Contractor Versions.
                li Allows VAV controls to control motor instead of a damper.
            a.btn.btn-secondary.products(href=baseUrl + 'new-products.html' type='button')
                | datasheet
    br
    br
    .row
        .col.product-image
            img.product-photos(src='../src/photos/products-photos/4spd_pro.png' alt='4SPD Control')
        .col.product-description
            h5 EVO/™ECM-4Spd-PRO (4 Speed Interface Unit)
            p.product-subheading Allows 24 Vac controls to select one of four adjustable flow indexes for an EC Motor.
            ul
                li Isolated Taps.
                li Fast or Gradual Speed Change.
                li Adjustment range is from Off to 100% of the programmed control range.
                li A fifth adjustment sets the flow index when no call is selected.
                li Pilot Pulse Enable/Disable.
                li PWM or 0-10 V output
            a.btn.btn-secondary.products(href=baseUrl + 'new-products.html' type='button')
                | datasheet
            a.btn.btn-secondary.products(href=baseUrl + 'new-products.html' type='button')
                | more on pro features
    br
    br
    .row
        .col.product-image
            img(src='' alt='')
        .col.product-description
            ul
                li EVO/™ECM-BCU (Bluetooth® Control Unit)
                li EVO/™BT Configurator (Windows Configurator Tool)
                li EVO Devices Android and iPhone Apps
            a.btn.btn-secondary.products(href=baseUrl + 'new-products.html' type='button')
                | see more
    br
    br
    .row
        .col.product-image
            img.product-photos(src='../src/photos/products-photos/CTC Plate.png' alt='CTC Control')
        .col.product-description
            h5 EVO/™ECM-CTC (Changeover Temperature Control)
            ul
                li Exhaust Fan Control
                li Whole house fan control
                li Outside Air Economizer
                li Discharge Air Temperature Control
                li Condenser Air Fan Control
            a.btn.btn-secondary.products(href=baseUrl + 'new-products.html' type='button')
                | datasheet
            a.btn.btn-secondary.products(href=baseUrl + 'new-products.html' type='button')
                | quick guide
    br
